    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  

<span data-ttu-id="5f82d-103">`IMemoryOwner<T>` 接口用于定义负责 <xref:System.Memory%601> 缓冲区的生存期管理的所有者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-103">The `IMemoryOwner<T>` interface is used to define the owner responsible for the lifetime management of a <xref:System.Memory%601> buffer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-104">`IMemoryOwner<T>` 接口的实例由 <xref:System.Buffers.MemoryPool%601.Rent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 方法返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-104">An instance of the `IMemoryOwner<T>` interface is returned by the <xref:System.Buffers.MemoryPool%601.Rent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="5f82d-105">虽然一个缓冲区可以有多个使用者，但在任何给定时间只能有一个所有者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-105">While a buffer can have multiple consumers, it can only have a single owner at any given time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-106">所有者可以：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-106">The owner can:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-107">直接或通过调用工厂方法来创建缓冲区。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-107">Create the buffer either directly or by calling a factory method.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-108">将所有权转移到另一个使用者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-108">Transfer ownership to another consumer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-109">在这种情况下，前一个所有者不应再使用该缓冲区。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-109">In this case, the previous owner should no longer use the buffer.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-110">当缓冲区不再使用时将其销毁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-110">Destroy the buffer when it is no longer in use.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="5f82d-111">由于 `IMemoryOwner<T>` 对象实现了 <xref:System.IDisposable> 接口，因此，只应在不再需要内存缓冲区并销毁它后，才调用其 <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-111">Because the `IMemoryOwner<T>` object implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface, you should call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method only after the memory buffer is no longer needed and you have destroyed it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-112">在对 `IMemoryOwner<T>` 对象的内存的引用可用时，*不*应释放该对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-112">You should *not* dispose of the `IMemoryOwner<T>` object while a reference to its memory is available.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5f82d-113">这意味着声明 `IMemoryOwner<T>` 的类型不应具有 <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5f82d-113">This means that the type in which `IMemoryOwner<T>` is declared should not have a <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.</span></span>

